OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPaid leave for premature   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbirths aims to be a relief 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffor parents                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Parents could take up to an extra 12   
OL,6, weeks of paid leave if their child is  
OL,7, born prematurely, as part of a new law.
OL,9,FBoth parents would qualify for one     
OL,10,Fweek's extra help - in addition to     
OL,11,Fexisting maternity and paternity leave 
OL,12,Fand pay entitlements - for every seven 
OL,13,Fdays their baby was in neonatal care.  
OL,15,FOne in seven UK newborns needs to be   
OL,16,Fplaced in a specialist hospital unit.  
OL,18,FThe Neonatal Care (Leave and Pay) Bill 
OL,19,Fcompleted its second reading in        
OL,20,FParliament last week.                  
